item.title: CVE-2020-2189|2024-08-04T07:01:41.129Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20scm%20filter%20jervis%20plugin
item.description: Jenkins SCM Filter Jervis Plugin 0.2.1 and earlier does not configure its YAML parser to prevent the instantiation of arbitrary types, resulting in a remote code execution vulnerability.
